==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: jūnzĭ yì yán, kuài mă yí biān
===Etymology===
Literally: If a gentleman says it, (it shall be done as if spurring) a fast horse (to gallop with) a single (strike of the) whip.
===Proverb===
'''[[君子]][[一]][[言]]，[[快]][[馬]][[一]][[鞭]]'''
# A gentleman's word is as good as gold.
===Alternative forms===
[[君子一言，快马一鞭]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
